                <p class="text-justify">The crew members at Avelo Airlines embrace their service and give their best to take good care of their customers. The <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/avelo-airlines-cancellation-policy.aspx">Avelo Airlines Cancellation Policy</a> is flexible. According to this policy, Avelo Airlines accepts the <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/cancellation-policy.aspx">cancellation of a reservation</a>. They do not charge a penalty if the cancellation is made within 24 hours after booking. One can change or cancel their flight 15 minutes before the scheduled departure time. </p>

                <h2>Cancellation Policy</h2>

                <p class="text-justify">If someone cancels their travel on Avelo within 24 hours of purchasing tickets, they do not need to pay the penalty and the amount is refunded. According to the original payment form, the airlines would provide a full refund if the purchase were made 7 days (168 hours) before the scheduled flight's departure time. </p>

                <p class="text-justify">You can receive and cancel Avelo Travel Funds that can be redeemed in the future <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/avelo-airlines.aspx">Avelo flight</a> in case of other reservations. You have the chance to change or cancel your scheduled flight depending on your condition before the departure time. If you face any problem and want to cancel your flight, call the Avelo Airline customer support center. </p>

                <h3>Frequently asked question</h3>

                <h3 class="text-justify">How much amount does Avelo charge to change a flight? </h3>
                <p class="text-justify">If the new ticket costs more than the previous ticket, you need to pay the difference in fare. If the new ticket costs less, the difference will be adjusted in the form of Avelo Travel Funds which can be used in the future as long as your travel is finished within one year from the first date of issue of your Travel funds. </p>
                <h3 class="text-justify">Is there any limit on the changes one can make? </h3>
                <p class="text-justify">No, there is no limit on the changes one can make in their flights. One can change their flights as many times as they want. But one thing that needs to be kept in mind is that one can be asked to pay a fare difference if the new ticket for a flight cost more than the previous ticket. </p>
                <h3 class="text-justify">Is there any time limit on the changes made or the cancellations? </h3>
                <p class="text-justify">Yes, there is a time limit on the changes or cancellations made on the flight. One has the chance to cancel or change their flight 15 minutes before the scheduled departure time. </p>
                <h3 class="text-justify">How can I check for my flight online? </h3>
                <p class="text-justify">The check-in process for Avelo Airlines is simple and not complicated. You can check your scheduled flight online on the official website of the airlines. You can also see your flight online at the avelo air mobile app. They also send an email within 24 hours of departure so you can check-in for your flight conveniently. </p>
                <h3 class="text-justify">Can I check in with a web-enabled device? </h3>
                <p class="text-justify">Yes, absolutely. You can check in with a web-enabled device and can check your flight status through devices like mobiles, laptops, and tablets. </p>



